videos.headline: Texas Tech's Dorsey picks off Murray on his first throw
videos.description: Texas Tech's defense comes up big as Vaughnte Dorsey intercepts Kyler Murray on his first throw of the game.

videos.headline: Texas Tech's Bowman throws a strike to Vasher for 6-yard TD
videos.description: Texas Tech gets on the board as Alan Bowman finds T.J. Vasher for a 6-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Murray gets picked off by Texas Tech's Murray for 2nd time
videos.description: Texas Tech's defense is dominating early as Vaughnte Dorsey picks off Kyler Murray for his 2nd interception of the game.

videos.headline: Henry powers through OU defense for 14-yard TD
videos.description: Texas Tech take advantage of great field position again as Jett Duffey finds Ta'Zhawn Henry for a 14-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Murray finds a wide-open Morris for 16-yard TD
videos.description: Oklahoma answers as Kyler Murray throws to a wide-open Lee Morris for a 16-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Oklahoma WR hangs on to the ball after taking a big hit
videos.description: Ohklahoma's Grant Calcaterra hangs on to the football after taking a nasty hit from Vaughnte Dorsey.

videos.headline: Murray escapes for 12-yard TD
videos.description: Kyler Murray eludes Texas Tech defenders for a 12-yard Oklahoma touchdown.

videos.headline: Ward walks in for 45-yard Texas Tech TD
videos.description: Alan Bowman throws to Da'Leon Ward who jukes an Oklahoma defender out of his shoes for an easy 45-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Sermon rushes in 5-yard TD
videos.description: Trey Sermon dashes up the middle of Texas Tech defense for a 5-yard Oklahoma touchdown.

videos.headline: Murray lobs it to Meier for an easy 5-yard TD
videos.description: Kyler Murray throws his 2nd touchdown of the half as he finds Carson Meier in the end zone to give the Sooners their first lead.

videos.headline: Texas Tech's Ward rushes in 1-yard TD
videos.description: A Big 12 shootout has begun as Texas Tech's Da'leon Ward answers with a 1-yard touchdown to give the Red Raiders' the lead going into the half.

videos.headline: Oklahoma trailing at the half to Texas Tech
videos.description: Kyler Murray totals three scores in the first half, but throws two interceptions and Oklahoma trails Texas Tech 31-28 at the half.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Oklahoma trailing at the half to Texas Tech) 2018/11/3 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Sermon gallops in 20-yard TD
videos.description: Trey Sermon gets free for a 20-yard Oklahoma touchdown.

videos.headline: Texas Tech converts on 4th down with 4-yard TD pass
videos.description: Texas Tech's gamble pays off as Jett Duffey finds Zach Austin for a 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Sooners take Red Raiders' 2-point conversion the other way
videos.description: Texas Tech fails to convert on 2-point conversion as Seth Collins throws a interceptions that is taken back the other way.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Sermon seals the game with 30-yard TD
videos.description: Trey Sermon escapes for a 30-yard touchdown, his 3rd of the game.

videos.headline: Riley: We had to 'find a way to win'
videos.description: Lincoln Riley discusses Kyler Murray's early struggles, throwing two interceptions and reacts to the Sooners' 51-46 win over the Red Raiders.

videos.headline: Murray, Oklahoma take showdown with Texas Tech
videos.description: Oklahoma takes a 51-46 win over Texas Tech behind four totals touchdowns from Kyler Murray and 323 rushing yards as a team.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Murray, Oklahoma take showdown with Texas Tech) 2018/11/3 ESHEET SOTFULL
